  "title": "CLINIC ASSISTANT",
  "description": "<ul>\n  <li>Assist in clinic’s day to day operations and functions.</li>\n  <li>Assist the Clinic Manager and Medical Director in the assigned clinic.</li>\n  <li>Responsible for all aspects of customer service including but not limited to cashiering, appointment booking, and answering customer enquiries.</li>\n  <li>Responsible for all matters pertaining to insurance, Medisave, and Letter of Guarantee(s).</li>\n  <li>Liaise with customers, vendors, suppliers, and local regulatory bodies when required.</li>\n  <li>Assist in the renewal of relevant licenses.</li>\n  <li>Other duties assigned by the Clinic Manager and/or Medical Director as required</li>\n</ul>",
